lead_paragraph: AL MVP Josh Donaldson and the Toronto Blue Jays are nearing agreement on a $28.65 million, two-year contract, according to a person familiar with the negotiations.

headline.print_headline: AP Source: Donaldson, Blue Jays Nearing $28.65M, 2-Year Deal
